Two Workers Found to Have High Radiation in Thyroid, Tokyo Electric Says

-- B y   T s u y o s h i   I n a j i m a
-- 
2011-05-30T03:09:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/two-workers-found-to-have-high-radiation-in-thyroid-tokyo-electric-says.html
Tokyo Electric Power Co. said two of
its Fukushima Dai-Ichi nuclear plant workers had high levels of
radiation in their thyroid glands.  The power utility is assessing the level of exposure,
according to a statement from Tokyo Electric today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tsuyoshi Inajima in Tokyo at 
